  "*** Westmarch Palace has been locked down ever since King Leoric took over ***": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "",
      "JP": "*** リオーレ王が権力を握って以来、西マーチ宮殿は厳重に防備されている ***",
